# No third-party IDE attribution

- Never add text such as **Made-with: Cursor**, "Made with Cursor", or similar tool/IDE attribution to commits (including trailers), pull request descriptions, UI copy, HTML, `README`, `CHANGELOG`, comments, or generated files.
- Prefer neutral, product-appropriate copy only (e.g. WhiteRock / Nerdshouse branding already used in the repo).
